{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dc996550a9","title":"关于主动加强统战工作的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"48acde00a1","index":0,"year":1943,"month":2,"day":7,"articleId":"dc996550a9"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji17","name":"毛泽东全集第17卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji17.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji17":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"eb20c40871","type":"paragraph","text":"关于主动加强统战工作的指示”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"dc996550a9"},{"id":"2ebfcfc661","type":"paragraph","text":"（1943年2月7日）国际国内的政治形势日趋好转，国方上层量仍采拖的办法，而其局部与下层已发现迫切需要与我党我军调整关系的现象：我们应不放松每一机会和每一小的事件，主动地加强局部统战工作，改善关系，以求更加促进国内整个形势的好转。各区应本此方针，按具体情况执行，并报告我们，如有磨擦事件，必须先经报告批准，不许自由行动","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"dc996550a9"},{"id":"6387fdebd7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛朱王叶","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"dc996550a9"},{"id":"67f7bc9ac5","type":"paragraph","text":"丑膜[1]这是毛泽东、朱德、王祥、叶剑英为主动加强统战工作致各战略","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"dc996550a9"}],"page":{"id":"ec73bee0fe","publicationId":"maoquanji17","articleId":"dc996550a9","start":507,"end":508}}}},"__N_SSG":true}